org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.hardware

Class Acquirer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.hardware.Mechanism
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.hardware.Acquirer

  • public class Acquirer
extends Mechanism
    Acquirer is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a robot's acquirer. Acquirer must be instantiated, then initialized using init() before being used. This class also contains autonomous actions involving the acquirer.
